<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                                                edel <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von
                                                Caspar Morspeken <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc.,
                                                das haben wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                                                und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr edel
                                                  <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir mit
                                                  <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan> Caspar Morspeken
                                                  <add><expan>sov<ex>er</ex>re</expan></add> in rede
                                                  <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> warn,
                                                  <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> er in
                                                  <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan> frist zu uns
                                                  <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz wir uns umb
                                                  <expan>sein<ex>en</ex></expan> dienst mit im
                                                geeynet wolten <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> frist nu
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>gang<ex>en</ex></expan> und für
                                                ist. Und wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel
                                                lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Egidii.</ab>
</div>
